			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=3>
				Large races, especially ogres and troll are hard to get into and move around in dungeons because they are to big to fit thru most passages. Unless you have a DE mask that is pre-nerfed, you are screwed. Another disadvantage is that they level the slowest. A halfing will make lvl 60 by the time a ogre makes 51.  Another disadvantage is when you are fighting in the planes, you can not hit your target because people are in your way because you are too fat. Another disadvantage is you cant wear all the armor small races have.  There is so many reasons that I'll stop here with these.  Big and stupid is not the best.		

