			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=3>
				All of the best weapons are armor are just as availible to big races as they are small races. So what do ogres and trolls get?  <br>  <br> Same AC, more HP, same weapon skills at the same level, more damage, they hit just as off and are hit just as often.  <br>  <br> What do wood elves or (as you mentioned) halfligns get? <br>  <br> Slightly more AC, less hp, same weapons skills despite higher intelligence, less damage, same likely hood of hitting/missing, same chance of being hit. <br>  <br> So I say again, large races have all the real advantages. The so called 'disadvantages' they have like tight squeezes and not being to get around near mobs are not disadvantages they are inconviences that are nothing major. Large races have huge advantages.		

